  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/google-search-traffic-incident-alerts/\"><img alt=\"A traffic incident in Google Now on Android\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/53d7b0ec9717bedf7d45547741bc0637/google-now-traffic-incident.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 443px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n不想被堵塞的交通耽误太多时间？Android 版 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googlesearch\">Google 搜索</a>最新加入的提醒功能或许会帮你省去不少这方面的烦恼。当你选择的路线中出现道路施工、事故或是其它可能会造成长时间延误的情况的话，Google 搜索便会通过 Google Now 发出提醒，让你可以提前考虑是否变更方向，转去一条更通畅些的道路。不过目前这项功能似乎仅在美国可用，不知 Google 未来有没有推广到其它地区的计划呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/24/google-search-traffic-incident-alerts/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+google/posts/WhNRboMLynU\" target=\"_blank\">Google (Google+)</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.googlequicksearchbox\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/google-search-traffic-incident-alerts/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20855804/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/google-search-traffic-incident-alerts/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
